[34.33821, "o", "# Product Vision: hello-helix\r\n\r\n## Mission\r\n\r\nProvide a simple, reliable command-line tool for temperature conversion that developers can use directly in terminals and scripts without friction.\r\n\r\n## Target User\r\n\r\nDevelopers and engineers who need quick temperature conversions during development, testing, and scripting workflows.\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nConverting between Celsius and Fahrenheit in a terminal currently requires:\r\n- Opening a calculator or browser\r\n- Installing a heavyweight utility\r\n"]
[34.338438, "o", "...\r\n\r\n"]
[36.339996, "o", "в”Ђв”Ђ docs/helix/01-frame/prd.md в”Ђв”Ђ\r\n"]
[36.341367, "o", "# PRD: hello-helix Temperature Converter\r\n\r\n## Overview\r\n\r\nA Node.js command-line tool for converting temperatures between Celsius and Fahrenheit.\r\n\r\n## Features\r\n\r\n### P0: Basic Conversion (MVP)\r\n\r\n- `convert --to-celsius <temp>` вЂ” Convert Fahrenheit to Celsius\r\n- `convert --to-fahrenheit <temp>` вЂ” Convert Celsius to Fahrenheit\r\n- Output formatted to one decimal place\r\n- Numeric input validation\r\n\r\n### P1: Input Validation & Error Messages\r\n\r\n- Detect non-numeric input and provide clear error messages\r\n- Report invalid flag usage\r\n- Suggest correct usage on error\r\n"]
[36.341664, "o", "...\r\n\r\n"]
[40.369022, "o", "\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n  ACT 4: Design вЂ” How to Build It\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n\r\n"]
