[252.071177, "o", "{\"type\":\"result\",\"subtype\":\"success\",\"is_error\":false,\"duration_ms\":16614,\"duration_api_ms\":16522,\"num_turns\":11,\"result\":\"## Project Review Summary\\n\\n### вњ… Strengths\\n- Core formulas correct; implementation follows design\\n- CLI parsing and error handling implemented\\n- Feature specs well-defined with clear acceptance criteria\\n- Clean, readable code without external dependencies\\n\\n### вљ пёЏ Issues & Gaps\\n\\n**Test Coverage:**\\n- Only 3 tests for 7 acceptance criteria (missing 98.6в†’37.0, 32в†’0.0, 0в†’32.0, 100в†’212.0, 37в†’98.6)\\n- Tests verify function return values as integers (32, 100) instead of formatted stringsвЂ”specs require \\\"exactly one decimal place\\\" output\\n- **No CLI integration tests** for flag parsing, exit codes, stdout/stderr, or error cases\\n\\n**Test-Spec Mismatch:**\\n- Test 1: `toFahrenheit(0)` expects `32` (number) not `\\\"32.0\\\"` (formatted string)\\n- Test 2: `toCelsius(212)` expects `100` (number) not `\\\"100.0\\\"` (formatted string)\\n- Test 3: `toCelsius(98.6)` uses tolerance check instead of exact format verification\\n\\n**Documentation:**\\n- TD-001 acceptance criteria remain unchecked (design shows `[ ]` boxes)\\n- No test documentation linking test cases to FEAT-001 stories\\n\\n**Code Length:**\\n- ~45 lines vs. ~40 line target in TD-001\\n\\n### рџ”§ What's Missing\\n1. Format-validation tests (`const result = toFahrenheit(0); assert.strictEqual(result.toFixed(1), \\\"32.0\\\")`)\\n2. CLI invocation tests (spawn child process, verify exit code/output)\\n3. Error case coverage (no flags, invalid flags, non-numeric input, multiple conflicting flags)\\n4. Checklist completion in TD-001\",\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"session_id\":\"fe199d87-bc99-4a97-a0e8-e7ec1ccacb88\",\"total_cost_usd\":0.035469850000000004,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":34,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":13269,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":98446,\"output_tokens\":1801,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":13269,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"},\"modelUsage\":{\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\":{\"inputTokens\":34,\"outputTokens\":1801,\"cacheReadInputTokens\":98446,\"cacheCreationInputTokens\":13269,\"webSearchRequests\":0,\"costUSD\":0.035469850000000004,\"contextWindow\":200000,\"maxOutputTokens\":32000}},\"permission_denials\":[],\"fast_mode_state\":\"off\",\"uuid\":\"6b4bfc7a-1d16-4d22-8952-1882e7fb9996\"}\r\n\r\n"]
